trans-unit.source: Represents a comparison operation applied to two arguments.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma operação de comparação aplicada a dois argumentos.

trans-unit.source: Equality, greater than, greater than or equal, less than, less than or equal, and inequality are comparison operations.
trans-unit.target: Igualdade, maior do que, igual ou superior, inferior que, menor que ou igual e inequality são as operações de comparação.
Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The DbComparisonExpression class requires that its arguments have a common result type.
trans-unit.target: A classe de DbComparisonExpression requer que os argumentos tenham um tipo de resultado comum.

trans-unit.source: This result type must be equality comparable for <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> and <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>; order comparable for <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> and <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>; and both for <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> and <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Este tipo de resultado tem de ser comparável em termos de igualdade <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>e <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>; comparável em termos de ordem <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>e <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>; e ambos para <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>e <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>.</xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind>

trans-unit.source: Implements the visitor pattern for expressions that do not produce a result value.
trans-unit.target: Implementa o padrão de visitantes de expressões que não produz um valor de resultado.
